<module>edoc_doclet_chunks</module>
<modulesummary>Doclet generating standalone
  EEP-48  
doc chunk files.</modulesummary>
<description>
<p>Doclet generating standalone
  <url href="https://www.erlang.org/erlang-enhancement-proposals/eep-0048.html">EEP-48</url>  
doc chunk files.</p>
 
  <p>Section <url href="chapter.html#Using_the_EDoc_API">Using the EDoc API</url>
  in the EDoc User's Guide shows an example of using this module.</p></description>
<funcs>
<func>
<name since="">run(Doclet_gen::<seeerl marker="edoc:edoc_doclet#type-command">edoc_doclet:command()</seeerl>, Ctxt::<seeerl marker="edoc:edoc_doclet#type-context">edoc_doclet:context()</seeerl>) -&gt; ok</name>
<fsummary>Main doclet entry point.</fsummary>

<desc><marker id="run-2"/>

<p>Main doclet entry point.</p>
 
  <p>This doclet is tightly coupled with <seeerl marker="edoc_layout_chunks">edoc_layout_chunks</seeerl>  
and should be used together with it.</p>
 
  <p>The only option this doclet accepts is <c>dir</c>, which controls
  where the <c>chunks</c> subdirectory and the EEP-48 chunk files will be placed.</p>
</desc></func></funcs>
